OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright, breezy and largely
OL,6,Fdry day. Cloudier in the morning but
OL,7,Fincreasingly sunny spells developing
OL,8,Fin the afternoon, especially in the
OL,9,Feast. Just a low chance of the odd
OL,10,Flight shower in the morning. Breezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry with some bright or sunny
OL,13,Fspells in the evening. Staying dry in
OL,14,Fthe east overnight with clear spells.
OL,15,FTurning cloudier in the west
OL,16,Fovernight, with a few light showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
