OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FBright spells and variable
OL,6,Fcloud with the odd light shower in the
OL,7,Fmorning. Drier for a time around the
OL,8,Fmiddle of the day before rain spreads
OL,9,Feast from late afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,12,Fchangeable, often cloudy and breezy
OL,13,Ffew days with spells of rain, but a
OL,14,Fgood deal of dry and bright weather in
OL,15,Fthe east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
